summary:
Es una raza practicamente igual que los nordicos solo que con diferentes habilidades, porfavor decidme que pensais sobre el mod
is a race very similar to the nords but with different habilities, please tell me what do you think
descriptionHtml:
PORFAVOR DECIDME QUE OS PARECE
PLEASE TELL ME WHAT DO YOU THINK ABOUT IT

Hablilidades: (Habilities)
arqueria +15 (archery +15)
sigilo +10 (sneak +10)
armadura ligera +5 (light armor +5)
a una mano +5 (one handed +5)

Poder:(power)
Lamar a la tormenta
Call storm
Limpiar cielos
Clear skies

NOTA: El aspecto es el mismo que los nordicos
NOTICE: the faces are the same as Nords

Instalacion: (instalation)
simplemente instalarlo en la carpeta data de skyrim
Just drop it in the skyrim/data folder
author: Frostyman03
